b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Designs.ai and Visme share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Brand Kit, Ai Generation. On the other hand, Visme uniquely offers Collaboration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Designs.ai holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Visme scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Visme comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Designs.ai begins at $29/mo. Visme stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Designs.ai requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
